data.description: EXTREMELY clean, VERY well cared for and NO HOA! Great open floor plan with lots of natural light. Vaulted ceilings in main living area AND Mastr Bdrm. Kitchen/Living/Dining and large Backyard/patio, PERFECT for entertaining! Back patio misting system. Walking dist to Buffalo Ridge Park with mtn hiking trails. North/South exp. Super close multi freeway access.  Matching granite counter tops and wood cabinets in Kitchen and both Baths. Fantastic schools! NEW garage door opener, toilets, microwave, stove, and dishwasher. Enjoy your gorgeous, tropical, front courtyard with beautiful shade covering (manually open and close with ease). Motion lights front/back.  Int/ext paint in excellent cond. Architectural shingle roof. This house has GREAT bones, checks all the boxes and WON'T last long!
